{
  "stem": "27770.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now about this week-- about the Gate of Heaven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We see there an article where this crazy guy, he was castrated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now one of the castrating experiment-- I have to tell you-- because that's what made me remind.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because otherwise, I would forget.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hitler's plan was that he will win the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after the war, anybody who hasn't got the blonde hair with the blue eyes, everybody will be his slave.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A slave, like a horse, who's going to work for Germany, use his power, his energy, and get the hell out from this world.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was his plan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now you know very well, if a horse or any animal who's castrated has more power than without it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he made an experiment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If it was 50, or 100 pair, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That they-- what they told me, the doctors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They took Jewish young boys and girls, from age 18 up to 25.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As I said, I don't remember if it's 50 or 100.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in order to make a castration, you need a hospital, you need a doctor, you need a nurse, you need all kind of facilities.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's too much money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For a Jew, a-- a Jew who doesn't deserve even a bullet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just need gas to destroy him what doesn't cost even a penny.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we'll make this operation with beautiful German engineering how to do this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have million of peoples, slaves after the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe the colored people, maybe the Mongolian, whoever-- whoever not Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this cost a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we have to prepare this already for after the war-- how to do this in mass production.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it shouldn't cost money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took a writing desk.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
